name: Traptrix Coronatus
desc: Unaffected by the effects of "Hole" Normal Trap Cards. When this card is Normal Summoned: You can add 1 "Traptrix" monster from your Deck to your hand. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 Set Spell/Trap Card you control; return that target to the hand, then you can Set 1 Spell/Trap Card from your hand.
